T10TD4192E:132a-26: rab tu dang ba ltar dang ba'i dad pa dang ldan pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-27: rtag tu bsil ba ltar nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las bsil ba dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-28: sprul gdug pa'i rnyi yis bag zhad med pa ltar dug gsum med pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-29: me'i 'jigs pa spangs pa ltar ngan 'gro'i 'jigs pa spangs pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-30: rang bzhin gyis rab tu gtsang ba ltar tshul khrims kyis gtsang ba dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-31: skom pa gcod pa ltar sred pa gcod pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132a-32: gru gzings 'degs pa'i khur bzod pa ltar gzhan don byed pa'i khur bzod pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-0: char sprin chen po lta bur chos drug dang ldan par gyis @132b shig ces brjod pa ni /
T10TD4192E:132b-1: khyod gcig ces tshigs su bcad pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:132b-2: dper na char sprin chen po des me tog la sogs pa la phan 'dogs pa ltar skye bo mang po sdig pa las bzlog ste /
T10TD4192E:132b-3: dge ba la bkod nas phan 'dogs pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-4: 'brug gi sgra sgrogs pa ltar 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis mi 'jigs pa dam pa'i chos smra ba'i sgra chen sgrogs pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-5: char chen po 'bab pa ltar grags pa rgya chen pos khyab pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-6: char de rlung gi shugs drag pos bskyod pa ltar sems snying rje'i rlung gis bskyod ba dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-7: sa'i rdul ldang ba zhi ba ltar nyon mongs pa'i rdul rab tu zhi bar byed pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-8: grib mas sa stengs brgyan pa ltar tshul khrims kyis sgo gsum brgyan pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-9: de ltar gdams ngag brjod nas /
T10TD4192E:132b-10: de las byung ba'i dge ba bsngo ba'i legs pa grub par bsngo ba ni /
T10TD4192E:132b-11: bdag gis zhes tshigs su bcad pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:132b-12: bde gshegs spyod pa ni dang po sems bskyed pa nas tha ma mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar ro //
T10TD4192E:132b-13: rtag tu bde pa ni ji srid 'tsho'i bar du nad med pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-14: longs spyod bzang po ni log par 'tsho ba med pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-15: yid la re ba 'byor pa ni 'dod pa'i don thams cad grub pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-16: gzhan la phan par dga' ba ni /
T10TD4192E:132b-17: sems can thams cad sdug bsngal las bsgral nas bde ba la 'god par spro ba'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-18: kun mkhyen ni shes bya thams cad thugs su chud pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-19: bgrod par shog ces pa ni de thob par smon pa'o //
T10TD4192E:132b-20: nyes pa zhi bar bsngo ba ni dmyal ba zhes tshigs su bcad pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:132b-21: dmyal ba'i dam grog dang g-yang sa lag mthil ltar mnyam mun nag rnam bsal lus la me 'bar ba rab tu zhi ba dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-22: ro myags btsog pa'i 'dam rdzab bskams nas der 'khrungs shing skyes pa'i padma'i lo mas khebs shing rtsa ba'i khye'u so thon pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-23: ro myags kyi 'dam de gtsang zhing dri zhim gyur nas /
T10TD4192E:132b-24: phyogs der padma kha bye bas sa rnams rnam par brgyan pa dang /
T10TD4192E:132b-25: dmyal ba rnams bde ba rgyas shing bsam pa bzang la rlung ser bu'i ngad bcas char zim 'bab pas tsha ba'i gdung ba zhi bar shog / sten pa 'byung bar bsngo ba ni /
T10TD4192E:133a-1: tshigs su bcad pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:133a-2: sgrogs pa ni dam pa'i chos ston pa'o //
T10TD4192E:133a-3: lha'i chu ni mtshe'u dal gyis 'bab pa'i //
T10TD4192E:133a-4: rtse mo ni der lha dang lha mo rnams rtse bas nang phan tshun dga' ba byed pa bas kyang gdul bya rnams dga' bar mdzad pa'o //
T10TD4192E:133a-5: gdul bya de dag kyang gang zhe na /
T10TD4192E:133a-6: lha dang mi 'dul ba zhes smos so //
T10TD4192E:133a-7: gang gi phyir gdul zhe na /
T10TD4192E:133a-8: skye shi zhes rkang pa phyed do //
T10TD4192E:133a-10: sangs rgyas dag ces rkang pa phyed dang gnyis so //
T10TD4192E:133a-11: brang pa bzhin du zhes bya ba ni gdul bya rnams gang la mos pa'i skur ro //
T10TD4192E:133a-12: nam zhar zhes bya ba ni rtag tu'o ;
T10TD4192E:133a-13: / bstan pa rgyas par bsngo ba ni /
T10TD4192E:133a-14: 'gro ba zhes rkang pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:133a-15: de'i 'gal rkyen med par bsngo ba ni //
T10TD4192E:133a-16: 'chi bdag ces rkang pa gcig go //
T10TD4192E:133a-17: mthun rkyen tshogs par bsngo ba ni 'phags pa'i zhes rkang pa gnyis so //
T10TD4192E:133a-18: 'phags pa'i skye bo ni sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang ;
T10TD4192E:133a-20: 'o na rang sangs rgyas 'phags pa'i skye bo ma yin nam zhe na /
T10TD4192E:133a-22: de ni lus kyis chos ston gyi ngag gis mi ston pas gtam tshogs med do //
T10TD4192E:133a-23: gtam tshogs ni theg pa gsum mo //
T10TD4192E:133a-24: spel ba ni gong nas gong du rgyas pa'o //
T10TD4192E:133a-25: de la phan yon ci yod ce na /
T10TD4192E:133a-26: zhi ba'i bdud rtsi zhes bya'o //
T10TD4192E:133a-27: zhi ba'i bdud rtsi'i char gyis bsil bas don byas shog / zhi ba'i bdud rtsi'i zla ba'i snang ba rab bzang don byas shog / ces tshig rnam par sbyar ro //
T10TD4192E:133a-28: bdag gis slob ma'i spring yig 'di //
T10TD4192E:133a-29: rtogs shing cung zad bshad pa las //
T10TD4192E:133a-30: dge ba dri med gang thob des //
T10TD4192E:133a-31: 'gro kun rnam par grol bar shog / slob ma la spring ba'i 'grel pa //
T10TD4192E:133a-32: slob dpon mkhas pa chen po shes rab 'byung gnas blo gros kyis rang gi slob ma rnams la phan pa'i don du mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T10TD4192E:133a-34: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi n'a ya tsan dra dang /
T10TD4192E:133a-35: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong chos kyi shes rab kyis sgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
